Buffer Sheet

Actions:

Add chapter
Add topic
Edit chapter
Edit topic
Delete chapter
Delete topic
Show Modal


State shape:

{
	chapters: [
		{
			id: moment().format(),
			name: "",
			standard: "",
			subject: "",
			topics: [{
				id: moment().format(),
				name: "",
			}],
		}
	]
	showModal: false,
	itemType: "",
	actionType: "",
	itemId: "",
	secondaryId: "",
	standard: "",
	subject: "",
}


State slices:

Slice 1 - Chapter (minus Topics):
{
	chapters: [{
		id,
		name,
		standard,
		subject,
	}]
}

Slice 2 - Topics:
{
	chapters: [{
		topics: [{
			id,
			name,
		}]
	}]
}

Slice 3 - Modal:
{
	showModal,
	itemType,
	actionType,
	itemId,
	secondaryId,
}

